WEBVTT

00:00:00.121 --> 00:00:02.037
Atceros, kā pie sevis nodomāju:

00:00:02.079 --> 00:00:05.371
"Šis pilnībā mainīs to,
kā mēs sazināmies."

00:00:05.413 --> 00:00:06.579
[Maza lieta.]

00:00:06.579 --> 00:00:07.746
[Liela ideja.]

00:00:08.996 --> 00:00:11.579
[Mārgareta Gulda Stjuarte par hipersaiti]

00:00:11.579 --> 00:00:14.121
Hipersaite ir saskarnes elements,

00:00:14.121 --> 00:00:15.538
un ar to es domāju,

00:00:15.538 --> 00:00:19.079
ka, lietojot telefona
vai datora programmatūru,

00:00:19.079 --> 00:00:21.246
aiz saskarnes ir ļoti daudz koda,

00:00:21.288 --> 00:00:24.663
kas instruē datoru, kā ar to rīkoties,

00:00:24.704 --> 00:00:27.704
taču šī saskarne ir tas,
ar ko cilvēki mijiedarbojas.

00:00:27.746 --> 00:00:30.579
Ja nospiežam uz šo, kaut kas notiek.